            <p class="tagline">一站式访问视频号、小红书和出海资源，高效便捷的内容导航平台</p>
            
            <div class="search-box">
                <input type="text" placeholder="搜索资源...">
                <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
            </div>
        </header>
        
        <div class="categories">
            <!-- 视频号板块 -->
            <div class="category">
